---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/base-layout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Genel Muayene - Kıymet Veteriner Kliniği | İzmir Bornova"
  description="Kıymet Veteriner Kliniği'nde profesyonel genel muayene hizmetleri. İzmir Bornova'da evcil dostlarınız için kapsamlı sağlık kontrolü ve tanı hizmetleri."
  keywords="genel muayene İzmir, Bornova veteriner muayene, kedi köpek muayene, veteriner kontrol, sağlık taraması"
>
  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <div
              class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-sky-800"
            >
              <svg
                class="mr-2 h-4 w-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              Genel Muayene
            </div>
            <h1 class="mb-6 text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Kapsamlı Sağlık Muayenesi
            </h1>
            <p class="mb-8 text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
              Evcil dostlarınızın genel sağlık durumunu değerlendirip,
              hastalıkların erken teşhisi için düzenli muayene hizmetleri
              sunuyoruz.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/randevu"
              class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-sky-600 px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-sky-700 hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              <svg
                class="mr-2 h-5 w-5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              Muayene Randevusu Al
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551601651-2a8555f1a136?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
              alt="Veteriner Muayene"
              class="h-96 w-full rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-2xl"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What's Included -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Muayenede Neler Yapılır?
          </h2>
          <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-xl text-gray-600">
            Kapsamlı muayene sürecimiz ile evcil dostunuzun sağlığını detaylı
            olarak değerlendiriyoruz
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div
            class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Fiziksel Muayene
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Gözler, kulaklar, burun, ağız, cilt ve tüy kontrolü. Kalp ritmi ve
              solunum dinleme.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-green-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Sağlık Geçmişi</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Aşı kayıtları, geçmiş hastalıklar, ilaç kullanımı ve beslenme
              alışkanlıkları değerlendirmesi.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-purple-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Vücut Ölçümleri
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Ağırlık, vücut sıcaklığı ölçümü ve genel fiziksel durum
              değerlendirmesi.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-orange-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Davranış Analizi
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Hayvanın davranış pattern'lerinin değerlendirilmesi ve stres
              faktörlerinin tespiti.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Koruyucu Bakım</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Gelecekteki sağlık sorunlarının önlenmesi için öneriler ve bakım
              planı oluşturma.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <div
              class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-red-500"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Erken Teşhis</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Hastalık belirtilerinin erken tespiti ve gerekli durumlarda ileri
              tetkik önerileri.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Muayene Süreci</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Adım adım muayene sürecimiz</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white"
            >
              1
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Karşılama</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Hayvanınızla tanışma ve sakinleştirme</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white"
            >
              2
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Anamnez</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Sağlık geçmişi ve şikayetlerin dinlenmesi
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white"
            >
              3
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Muayene</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Detaylı fiziksel muayene</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 text-2xl font-bold text-white"
            >
              4
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Rapor</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Bulgular ve öneriler</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Muayene Ücretleri
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Şeffaf ve uygun fiyatlarla hizmet</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-4xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 text-center shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Temel Muayene</h3>
            <div class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-sky-600">₺200</div>
            <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Genel fiziksel muayene</li>
              <li>✓ Ağırlık ve sıcaklık ölçümü</li>
              <li>✓ Temel sağlık değerlendirmesi</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="scale-105 transform rounded-3xl bg-sky-600 p-8 text-center text-white shadow-lg"
          >
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Kapsamlı Muayene</h3>
            <div class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold">₺350</div>
            <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>✓ Detaylı fiziksel muayene</li>
              <li>✓ Kalp ve solunum dinleme</li>
              <li>✓ Deri ve tüy kontrolü</li>
              <li>✓ Beslenme önerileri</li>
            </ul>
            <div
              class="inline-block rounded-full bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-white"
            >
              En Popüler
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 text-center shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Premium Muayene
            </h3>
            <div class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-sky-600">₺500</div>
            <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Tam kapsamlı muayene</li>
              <li>✓ Temel laboratuvar testleri</li>
              <li>✓ Rapor ve öneriler</li>
              <li>✓ 1 hafta takip</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section
      class="mb-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 to-blue-700 py-20 text-white"
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center lg:px-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">
          Evcil Dostunuzun Sağlığını Kontrol Ettirin
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-xl opacity-90">
          Düzenli muayeneler ile hastalıkları erken teşhis edin ve sevgili
          dostunuza sağlıklı bir yaşam sunun.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="/randevu"
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-white px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-sky-600 shadow-lg transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <svg
              class="mr-2 h-5 w-5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Muayene Randevusu Al
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:+905551234567"
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border-2 border-white px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white hover:text-sky-600"
          >
            <svg
              class="mr-2 h-5 w-5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Hemen Ara
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
